23073 committee of the whole meeting notice Wednesday, April 26, 2023 at 6 p.m. Mr. Clerk, please call the roll. Vice president affairs. Yes, here present. Sorry. Councilor Collins. Present. Councilor Knight. Councilor Knight is absent. Councilor Scarpelli. Councilor Scarpelli is informed as he's not gonna be able to attend this evening. Councilor Sanz. Present.

