The purpose of this meeting is to discuss the capital improvement plan presentation, paper 23-073. The committee has invited Mayor Brianna Longo-Kern and Chief of Staff Nina Nazarian to attend this meeting. For further information, aids and accommodations, contact the city clerk at 781-393-2425. Sincerely yours, Nicole Murrell, Council President. The meeting notice says just what we're here for. I believe actually in lieu of members of the administration, we'd have Sarah Kincannon from the Collins Center, who is able to give us a presentation on the capital improvement plan

4
00:01:11,682 --> 00:01:40,876
Sarah, I believe you should have the ability to share your screen at this point. Excellent. Thank you. Let me share my screen. How does that look? Can everyone see it? And is it big enough? Yes and yes.

